        <Parent_String>albumen prints [300127121], photographic prints by process [300138213], photographic prints [300127104], positives (photographs) [300138191], photographs by form [300127008], photographs [300046300], visual works by material or technique [300191091], visual works (works) [300191086], Visual Works (hierarchy name) [300179869], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
